			<div class="content" id="post-content-1055654">
									

<p>Hrrrm. I don't know.</p>
<p>Basic idea of a sickness that spontaneously appears and disappears based on location … that's not so bad.</p>
<p>The execution is too sloppy to get a reaction out of me. All that stuff at the end is just confusing as opposed to being something that hammers the fear (or wonder) home. There's a … smiley emoticon in there… and… nnnneugh.</p>
<p>If you need to refer to the Foundation in a document call it the Foundation rather than the SCP. The SCP is what we do, the Foundation is what we are.</p>

